    %% Telemetry egress
    TracingMW -->|"HTTP/4318<br/>OTLP<br/>No Auth"| OTEL

    %% External API egress
    OtherEP -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key"| OpenAI
